relation: A vehicle of evil to procreate evil and bring evil forth upon this small and innocent world. Let there be light!

Based on the obscure Mother 3 enemy, that wasn't even in the finished game. I used two ping-pong balls, some tape and a Chistmas tree. It was awesome but I have to go take it down before it burns down or my parents find out I put two ping-pong balls on the tree.
